_sText:
Well this is simply a map i had no real high hopes for when i began with it mainly just something to pass the time with but i did manage to make something out of it where as the original idea and layout has stayed the same as my original sketch i created a new look on it by adding a sort of-travel inbetween worlds feel- which im sure has been done in other maps before but i like my small take on it :D 

i hope you enjoy it. just to note you cant shoot through the glass/fence/ladders the lights in the aquarium-ish room can bet turned off:P

i'll include the nav but it is the custom built nav so it doesn't work to well..
